snippet.title: Amber locks Mikmik | Nang Ngumiti Ang Langit (With Eng Subs)
snippet.description:
Amber (Krystal Mejes) locks Mikmik (Sophia Reola) in the store room and stops Britney (Heart Ramos) and Joseph (Miguel Vergara) from finding their friend. (With English Subtitles)
